*Neverovatno* je koliko je on napredovao u poslednjih nekoliko meseci. (It's incredible how much he has advanced in the last few months.)

Njegovo *neverovatno* umeće bilo je zapanjujuće. (His incredible skill was astonishing.)

On je veoma talentovan i *neverovatno* je strpljiv. (He is very talented and incredibly patient.)

Njegovo *neverovatno* postignuće nadmašilo je sve očekivanja. (His incredible achievement exceeded all expectations.)

Njegov *neverovatno* uspeh je zaslužan. (His incredible success is deserved.)